descriptionHtml:
To purchase Eden Smart Modules, please mail us on business@edensmarthomes.com

HomeID and password are required to access the app, which are provided to Eden Smart Homes hardware users

Control all your existing appliances (Lights, Fan, Geyser, AC etc.) from anywhere around the world using your smartphone

You can:

a) Control all your existing appliances (lights, Fans, AC, Geyser etc.) using your mobile
b) Check their status in real time even if they are controlled using manual switches
c) Schedule them to daily turn on/off automatically
d) Get real-time notifications when they are turned ON/OFF
e) Create custom scenarios, so a group of appliances can be controlled using single command
descriptionShort: ** This app is only meant for users of Eden Smart Modules **
